{"address1": "Mumbai-Pune Road", "address2": "Pimpri", "city": "Pune", "zip": "411018", "country": "India", "phone": "91 20 2710 1000", "fax": "91 20 2742 6000", "website": "https://www.ksb.com/en-in", "industry": "Specialty Industrial Machinery", "industryKey": "specialty-industrial-machinery", "industryDisp": "Specialty Industrial Machinery", "sector": "Industrials", "sectorKey": "industrials", "sectorDisp": "Industrials", "longBusinessSummary": "KSB Limited manufactures and sells power-driven pumps and industrial valves in India and internationally. It operates through Pumps and Valves segments. The Pumps segment manufactures and trades in industrial pumps, submersible pumps, effluent treatment pumps, etc.; and provides related spares and services. The Valves segment is involved in the manufacture and trading of industrial valves; and provision of related spares and services. It offers spare parts kits, mechanical seals, valve actuator and automation products, pump automation, mixers, motors, process monitoring service, and body pressure relief valves. The company also provides technical services comprising consultancy and analysis services, such as technical consultancy, energy efficiency consulting, identification of energy-saving potential, SES system efficiency service, and well pump measurement; installation and commissioning; operation services, including inspection service, maintenance inspection management, total pump management, spare parts inventory management, pump monitoring from specialists, and service for automation products; pump, motor, and valve repair services, as well as retrofit, reverse engineering, 3D printing, service for other rotating equipment, and service for mechanical seals; and conducts seminars and training sessions. Its products are used in wastewater, water, and industry technology; chemicals production; building services; energy technology; mining; dredge; oil and gas technology; and decarbonization applications. The company was formerly known as KSB Pumps Limited and changed its name to KSB Limited in June 2018. KSB Limited was incorporated in 1960 and is headquartered in Pune, India.", "companyOfficers": [{"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Rajeev Jayantiprasad Jain", "age": 61, "title": "MD, Executive Director & Regional Executive Officer - Region Asia West", "yearBorn": 1964, "fiscalYear": 2024, "totalPay": 55455000, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Mahesh Gopal Bhave", "title": "CFO, VP of Finance, Purchase & DTC", "fiscalYear": 2024, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Nandan B. Paranjape M.Tech", "age": 71, "title": "Director of Operations", "yearBorn": 1954, "fiscalYear": 2024, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Ms. Shraddha Sham Kavathekar", "title": "Company Secretary & Compliance Officer", "fiscalYear": 2024, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Prashant  Kumar", "title": "Vice President of Sales & Marketing", "fiscalYear": 2024, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Mohan  Patil", "title": "Vice President of Human Resources", "fiscalYear": 2024, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Pradeep V. Watve", "age": 61, "title": "Head of Foundry Operations", "yearBorn": 1964, "fiscalYear": 2024, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Shirish K. Kulkarni", "age": 63, "title": "Director of Human Resource & Industrial Relations - Irrigation and Process Division (IPD)", "yearBorn": 1962, "fiscalYear": 2024, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. V. Ravi Shanker", "age": 69, "title": "General Manager of Budgeting & Controlling", "yearBorn": 1956, "fiscalYear": 2024, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}], "compensationAsOfEpochDate": 1735603200, "executiveTeam": [], "maxAge": 86400, "priceHint": 2, "previousClose": 782.3,